Django admin templates customized to use twitter bootstrap

Can be customized like defaults admin templates

AUTHOR
Guilherme Kuhn <g.kuhn0@gmail.com>

INSTALLATION
1. Make a simbolic link (or copy template folder) in your project root.
cd PROJECT_ROOT
ln -s FOLDER_WHERE_IS_README/admin_bootstrap admin_bootstrap

2. Put in your settings.py:
TEMPLATE_DIRS = (
    'FULL_PATH_TO_PROJECT/admin_bootstrap',
    # other template paths
)


